body:
Unfortunately looks like this patch does not take advantage of slf4j parameterized logging [1].

Either do like:

log.info("=================================" + "\nTest " + description + " is running." + "\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------");
or:

log.info("===============================" + "\nTest {} is running." + "\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------", description);

[1] http://www.slf4j.org/faq.html#logging_performance
